    <body>
		<div class="Example">
        <h6>Example: Referencing values from an earlier message</h6>
        <p>The following action can be used to log the length of an SSH session (the time difference between a login and a logout message in the context):</p><pre>&lt;actions&gt;
    &lt;action&gt;
        &lt;message&gt;
            &lt;values&gt;
                &lt;value name="MESSAGE"&gt;An SSH session for ${SSH_USERNAME}@1 from ${SSH_CLIENT_ADDRESS}@2 closed. Session lasted from ${DATE}@2 to ${DATE} &lt;/value&gt;
            &lt;/values&gt;
        &lt;/message&gt;
    &lt;/action&gt;
&lt;/actions&gt;</pre>
			</div>
    </body>
</html>